author: Lan Pitts
title: WWE: Top 5 Greatest Women Managers
text:
WWE: Top 5 Greatest Women Managers Lan Pitts Slide of 
Behind every great man is a greater woman. 
No matter the moniker of Diva, manager, or valet, there's absolutely no doubt that some of the greatest wrestlers of all time had their best moments when they were assisted or had the benefit of a woman at ringside. Some of have been gorgeous beyond words, others were as hard as a diamond. 
With March being International Women's Month, it's more than apt that we take a look at the best of the best that made good men great and, in some cases, outshone their male counterpart. Who all paved the way for the women of the future of the industry and provided some of the best moments WWE has ever had? 
Let's take a look at the five most influential and greatest women managers of all time, starting with a rather contemporary number.
